## 🚨 Important Update: SN30 Deregistration & TAO Refund 🚨

GM @deleted-role 

**We made the difficult decision to deregister Subnet 30. Here's why:**
- Scaling issues led to slow generation times
- Other subnets emerged with similar focus
- Our vision evolved beyond SN30's original scope

But every ending, has a new beginning! We're launching Subnet 39: EdgeMaxxing. (See here @deleted-role)

Our mission is to enable millions to contribute their computing power using their everyday devices (Macbooks, Gaming computers, Smartphones, etc.). This new subnet is better aligned with Bittensor's structure, incentives, and decentralized AI vision. 

Some Important Notes:

- 📢 TAO Refund for Miners We're issuing a TAO refund to all SN30 miners who were registered at the time of dissolution. Each eligible miner will receive an equal share of the 100 TAO refund pool. This refund will be processed by Wednesday, July 9th, Noon EDT.
- 🙏 We've donated 400 $TAO to community members who've contributed significantly to the Bittensor ecosystem. See more: https://x.com/WOMBO/status/1808882191939645493
- 🚀 What's Next? Head over to the new SN39 channel to learn about EdgeMaxxing and how you can get involved: https://discord.com/channels/799672011265015819/1241046233800507482

Thanks for being part of the SN30 journey. Your support and contributions have been invaluable ❤️

Onwards! 🫡🫡🫡
